data.description: Welcome Home! Contemporary 4/2.5 with 3,950 sq ft off Scenic Hwy near I-10 with a beautiful view of Escambia Bay. Large great room with 18' cathedral ceiling, fireplace, soaring windows with loads of natural light, and sliding glass door to the new deck. There's a formal dining room off of the great room and a half bath for guests. There's an updated kitchen with custom cabinets with sliding shelves, granite countertops, stainless appliances, tile backsplash, pantry, coffee bar, wine racks, wine cooler, and wood ceiling with recessed lights. Large breakfast room that leads into an 18x18 sun room with wood ceiling and a sliding glass door to the outside entertaining area. The downstairs primary bedroom features its own HVAC and a grand closet that could double as a study/office/gym, with Pella windows, skylights, and private entrance to the backyard. The primary bathroom has double vanities, a whirlpool tub big enough for two, separate shower, two more closets, and its own water heater. A spiral staircase leads upstairs to a bonus/sitting room with a catwalk, three spare bedrooms, and a full bathroom. The laundry room is off of the kitchen, with front loader washer & dryer that convey, custom cabinets, and folding area. There's a swing-in oversized 2-car garage with 240v outlets for your EV, additional driveway parking, and privacy fenced yard. Whisper Way is a beautiful neighborhood of gently-rolling hills and mature, twisting live oaks. It's only a 20-min drive to Pensacola Beach or 10 mins downtown along the historic Scenic Hwy, and just a half mile from the I-10 onramp. 3-HVAC units installed in 2018, New Roof in 2021, new deck in 2021, New LVP flooring in 2019, Freshly painted interior, and new carpet in 2023. Contact me or your agent today to learn more about this beautiful home.
